text: Patrick Bihetoué Arnaud Malo (born 18 February 1992) is a Burkinabé professional footballer who plays as a left-back for Kuwaiti club Qadsia SC and the Burkina Faso national team. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Burkinabé footballers Category:People from Ouagadougou
title: Patrick Malo
